rrelations among\nthe observables. Furthermore, we identify benchmark points which are in fact\nable to explain all three anomalies ($b \\to c \\tau \\nu$, $b\\to s\\ell^+\\ell^-$\nand $a_\\mu$), without violating bounds from other observables, and study their\npredictions for future measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2019 18:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 15:16:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Oct 2020 12:28:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-19"}
